data.description: Don't miss your chance to own this gorgeous, updated home located on Windward Island! Enjoy views of the Tidal creek while being close to shopping and more. There is no need to worry about lugging groceries up the stairs, there is an elevator! This home is equipped with wood flooring throughout, updated kitchen and baths, a fully screened in back porch, and a fenced in backyard. New HVAC was installed at the end of 2022. Property listed under appraised value! Professional photos will be uploaded on 04/09/2024.
